						<additions>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Shemu᾿el of Sha῾ar Arieh</name>: inscribed, folio 20r. Folio 264v contains the same former owner's note (written twice) in Hebrew in a romanized transcription, stating that the manuscript was bought from <name type="person" role="owner">Solomon Foa</name>.</p>
							<p>Folio 20r is a title-page, probably added later in the 17th century.</p>
